LanguageData.VFEArch_WoodLog_Walnut.label: walnut
LanguageData.VFEArch_WoodLog_Walnut.description: Wood from trees or other fibrous plants. Useful for building structures and weapons. It is a good fuel for campfires and generators, and can be refined into chemfuel. In a pinch, a piece of wood can be used as a weapon or a leg.
